data.description: Here it is! This two story 5 bedroom 3 bath gated community sits on .32 of an acre. Just imagine sitting on the back front porch each morning watching the sunrise with your cup of coffee and ending your day watching the sunset with a glass of wine from the master bedroom deck that spans the entire width of the home! This suburban master piece also features a huge open kitchen and nook with unobstructed views of the family room, and media area. It boasts large rooms, a formal living room, a formal dining room, and so much more.  There is a large media room situated near the kitchen to enjoy your favorite movies with your love ones.  New sod 2022, Pressure washed 2022, AC 2017, New Fridge, 2017, New Stove, 2017, New garage doors, 2017. It is a must that you view this home!!! There is nothing that can compare in this price point! Near Publix and Lowes, come today and make an offer on this beauty.
